emi Panarin]], Chicago Blackhawks\n|-\n| align=center | [[Winger (ice hockey)|RW]]\n|[[Patrick Kane]], Chicago Blackhawks\n|[[Vladimir Tarasenko]], St. Louis Blues\n| align=center | [[Forward (ice hockey)|F]]\n|[[Connor McDavid]], Edmonton Oilers\n|-\n| align=center | [[Winger (ice hockey)|LW]]\n|[[Jamie Benn]], Dallas Stars\n|[[Alexander Ovechkin]], Washington Capitals\n| align=center | [[Forward (ice hockey)|F]]\n|[[Jack Eichel]], Buffalo Sabres\n|-\n|}\n\n==Milestones==\n\n===First games===\n<!-- Do not add more players unless they meet notability requirements as outline here: [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Ice Hockey/NHL season pages format#Debuts and Last Games]] -->\nThe following is a list of notable players who played their first NHL game during the 2015\u201316 season, listed with their first team.\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:15em\"| Player !! style=\"width:15em\"| Team !! style=\"width:25em\"| Notability\n|-\n| [[Connor McDavid]] || [[Edmonton Oilers]] || [[List of first overall NHL draft picks|First overall pick in the 2015 Draft]]\n|-\n| [[Artemi Panarin]] || [[Chicago Blackhawks]] || [[Calder Memorial Trophy]] winner\n<!-- Do not add more players unless they meet notability requirements as outline here: [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Ice Hockey/NHL season pages format#Debuts and Last Games]]. Very few will qualify during the season -->\n|}\n\n===Last games===\n<!-- Do not add more players unless they meet notability requirements as outline here: [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Ice Hockey/NHL season pages format#Debuts and Last Games]] -->\nThe following is a list of players of note who played their last NHL game in 2015\u201316, listed with their team:\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:15em\"| Player !! style=\"width:15em\"| Team !! style=\"width:25em\"| Notability\n|-\n|[[Niklas B\u00e4ckstr\u00f6m|Niklas Backstrom]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.hifk.fi/uutiset/tiedote-niklas-baeckstroem-ja-juhamatti-aaltonen-ifkhon | title = Niklas Backstro